items.title: Soleil Hoodie - Sunset
items.caption: Soleil Hoodie - Sunset
items.description:
Sunny days are ahead in our ultimate Faherty hoodie. Made from a super-soft and lightweight French terry, this where everywhere layer is pieced together in a sun, sea, and sand motif that channels all the feel-good vibes.


Fit: Relaxed fit

Detail: Long sleeve hoodie with a fun in-the-sun inpired Pieced Design

Material: 100% Cotton

Model: Monika is 5’9 wearing size Small 


Care: Turn inside out. Machine Wash cold with like colors. Gentle cycle. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low. Remove promptly. Cool iron when needed.
WKS2336-UNT
